城市的建造，本来也是因萨尔瓦多雷与叙拉古的缘分而起，家父也只是希望她能够回到叙拉古看看这座城市。","id":145,"figure":["avg_427_vigil_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":146},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"唉，不愧是贝洛内家。","id":147,"figure":["avg_npc_695_1",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"明知德克萨斯这个姓氏对罗塞蒂家族来说意义重大，却就这样落落大方地请了回来。","id":148,"figure":["avg_npc_695_1",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"大气，真的大气。","id":149,"figure":["avg_npc_695_1",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"我瓦拉赫今天算是服了。","id":150,"figure":["avg_npc_695_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":151},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"你又在开玩笑了。","id":152,"figure":["avg_427_vigil_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"玩笑？这哪里是玩笑？","id":154,"figure":["avg_npc_695_1",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"切利尼娜小姐还活着的消息，对我们罗塞蒂来说意义非凡。","id":155,"figure":["avg_npc_695_1",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"不管贝洛内怎么想，罗塞蒂都欠你们一次。","id":156,"figure":["avg_npc_695_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"我们两家是将来要共同建设新城市的关系，有什么欠与不欠的？","id":158,"figure":["avg_427_vigil_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"哈哈哈，好，说得好啊！","id":160,"figure":["avg_npc_695_1",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"看来，老弟你早就在这等着我了。","id":161,"figure":["avg_npc_695_1",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"说吧，你想要什么？","id":162,"figure":["avg_npc_695_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":163},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"我要的东西很简单——","id":164,"figure":["avg_427_vigil_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":165},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"罗塞蒂不要插手这件事。","id":166,"figure":["avg_427_vigil_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":167},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"哦？要我们眼睁睁地看着最后的德克萨斯被审判，我恐怕没有办法向首领交代。","id":168,"figure":["avg_npc_695_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":169},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"等到审判结束后，她会被收押，你们仍然可以见到她。","id":170,"figure":["avg_427_vigil_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":171},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"......只是见到她吗？","id":172,"figure":["avg_npc_695_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":173},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"她是我们的客人，但她也可以是罗塞蒂的客人。","id":174,"figure":["avg_427_vigil_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"......好，成交！","id":176,"figure":["avg_npc_695_1",4]},{"type":"dialog","id":177},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":178},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":179},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":180},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/11/Avg_bg_bg_bar_1.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":181},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":182},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":183},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_690_1#7$1","fadetime":"1","id":184},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"......","id":186,"figure":["avg_npc_690_1",6]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"没想到，在这里把切利尼娜搬了出来。","id":187,"figure":["avg_npc_690_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_690_1#8$1","id":188},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"是拉维妮娅的想法吗？不......她不会不知道，切利尼娜不是凶手。","id":189,"figure":["avg_npc_690_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"以她的性格，她不会做出这个决定。","id":190,"figure":["avg_npc_690_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_690_1#7$1","id":191},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"难道是莱昂说服了她？","id":192,"figure":["avg_npc_690_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_690_1#3$1","id":193},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"......算了，无论如何，没想到还有这一手。","id":194,"figure":["avg_npc_690_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_698_1#1$1","id":195},{"type":"dialogue","name":"家族成员","text":"......德米特里，现在，我们应该怎么办？","id":196,"figure":["avg_npc_698_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"家族成员","text":"要去暗杀切利尼娜吗？","id":197,"figure":["avg_npc_698_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_690_1#9$1","id":198},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"......你知道在七年前那场乱子里，有多少家族的精锐折在她手上吗？","id":199,"figure":["avg_npc_690_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_698_1#1$1","id":200},{"type":"dialogue","name":"家族成员","text":"但——","id":201,"figure":["avg_npc_698_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_690_1#8$1","id":202},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"偷袭、爆炸，或者干脆下毒，或许我们总有些办法......","id":203,"figure":["avg_npc_690_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"可别忘了，她归根结底是谁请回来的人。","id":204,"figure":["avg_npc_690_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_690_1#9$1","id":205},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"无论是谁的主意，这确实很聪明。","id":206,"figure":["avg_npc_690_1",8]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"事已至此，只能用一些粗暴的办法让审判中止了。","id":207,"figure":["avg_npc_690_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_698_1#1$1","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"家族成员","text":"......","id":209,"figure":["avg_npc_698_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_690_1#3$1","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"归根结底，我们的目的是让城里乱起来。","id":211,"figure":["avg_npc_690_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_690_1#9$1","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"从一开始，挑衅西西里夫人就在我们的计划之中。","id":213,"figure":["avg_npc_690_1",8]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"现在，也只不过是把这一步提前了而已。","id":214,"figure":["avg_npc_690_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_698_1#1$1","id":215},{"type":"dialogue","name":"家族成员","text":"......是。","id":216,"figure":["avg_npc_698_1",0]},{"type":"character","id":217},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"我倒觉得，还有别的方法哦。","id":218},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_690_1#7$1","id":219},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":220},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"谁？！","id":221,"figure":["avg_npc_690_1",6]},{"type":"dialog","id":222},{"type":"character","id":223},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_683_1#3$1","fadetime":"1","id":224},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":225},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"这么有趣的事情，能让我也参加一下吗？","id":226,"figure":["avg_npc_683_1",2]},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":227},{"type":"dialog","id":228},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":229},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":230},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":231},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/74/Avg_bg_33_g11_mansionhall.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":232},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$distressed_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_distressed_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":233,"musicid":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":234},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":235},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#2$1","fadetime":"0.5","id":236},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":237},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝纳尔多","text":"......","id":238,"figure":["avg_npc_685_1",1]},{"type":"dialog","id":239},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#2$1","focus":"-1","id":240},{"type":"playsound","key":"$doorknockquite","id":241},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":242},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#1$1","id":243},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝纳尔多","text":"请进。","id":244,"figure":["avg_npc_685_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":245},{"type":"playsound","key":"$dooropenquite","id":246},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":247},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":248},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":249},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"总监，德克萨斯的事情您知道了吗？！","id":250,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#6$1","focus":"1","id":251},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝纳尔多","text":"我也是刚刚得知。","id":252,"figure":["avg_npc_685_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":253},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"您知道什么内幕吗？","id":254,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#6$1","focus":"1","id":255},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝纳尔多","text":"至少以我得到的消息来说，是拉维妮娅法官亲口宣布的。","id":256,"figure":["avg_npc_685_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":257},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"拉维妮娅，是那位帮助过我的法官小姐......","id":258,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":259},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"她......不像是会说谎的人，但是......","id":260,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#6$1","focus":"1","id":261},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝纳尔多","text":"你想要推掉你的首秀吗？","id":262,"figure":["avg_npc_685_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":263},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"您......能帮我想一想办法吗？","id":264,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"我想......至少先见一见她。","id":265,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#6$1","focus":"1","id":266},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝纳尔多","text":"且不论你的首秀是否可以推迟......","id":267,"figure":["avg_npc_685_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝纳尔多","text":"我想知道的是，见到了又如何呢？","id":268,"figure":["avg_npc_685_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":269},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"......","id":270,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#6$1","focus":"1","id":271},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝纳尔多","text":"空小姐，我还记得，你曾经说过，你是为了与她重逢才与另外两个朋友一起来到叙拉古。","id":272,"figure":["avg_npc_685_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝纳尔多","text":"你一直相信着，你所见到的她，就是真正的她。","id":273,"figure":["avg_npc_685_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#6$1","focus":"1","id":274},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝纳尔多","text":"但现在，你已经知道，她隐藏的过去究竟如何。","id":275,"figure":["avg_npc_685_1",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝纳尔多","text":"你被迫发现，你所追逐的那个人，或许与你的想象相去甚远。","id":276,"figure":["avg_npc_685_1",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝纳尔多","text":"见到她，又能怎么样呢？","id":277,"figure":["avg_npc_685_1",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝纳尔多","text":"你能对她说些什么，她又能对你说些什么？","id":278,"figure":["avg_npc_685_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":279},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"......如果真的是这样，那么恐怕，擅自想象的我也有责任，或许是我对她还不够了解。","id":280,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#6$1","focus":"1","id":281},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝纳尔多","text":"明明是对方对你有所隐瞒？","id":282,"figure":["avg_npc_685_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":283},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"这也要看对方有没有理由呀。","id":284,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":285},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"不管怎么说，贝纳尔多先生，在演艺圈这个大染缸里，我也算是见识过许多人啦。","id":286,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",6]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"要做到表里如一实在是太难了，至少我认为我是做不到的。","id":287,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",6]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"我总是在想，有一天我也会变得身不由己的。","id":288,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",6]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"所以，我从来都不会去要求别人这么做。","id":289,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",6]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"每个人都会有秘密，我也有，她也有，想必，您也会有。","id":290,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",6]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"如果对方将他想要展现给我的一面贯彻到底，这难道不也是一种真诚吗？","id":291,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":292},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝纳尔多","text":"......诚然。","id":293,"figure":["avg_npc_685_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":294},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"而且，或许是我那时候没有说清楚吧。","id":295,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"我来找德克萨斯，不是想要责备她，不是的。","id":296,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":297},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"我们四个一起在龙门生活了快六年了。","id":298,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"这六年的生活对我来说是弥足珍贵的。","id":299,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"而我至少相信，对她来说，也是这样。","id":300,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"即使如此，她却依然不告而别。","id":301,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":302},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"我应该为此愤怒吗？","id":303,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":304},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"不，我很担心她。","id":305,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":306},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"能天使和可颂也是这样的。","id":307,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":308},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"所以，我们才会来到叙拉古。","id":309,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",6]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"如果她被卷进了麻烦的事情里，那我们就去帮助她脱身。","id":310,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",6]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"如果她的过去沉重到能够压垮她，那我们就去和她一起承担。","id":311,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":312},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝纳尔多","text":"众多剧作中，关于切利尼娜的末路虽然只是谣传，但德克萨斯家族的末路却是众所周知。","id":313,"figure":["avg_npc_685_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝纳尔多","text":"她的过去恐怕比你想象的要深重得多。","id":314,"figure":["avg_npc_685_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":315},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"我知道。","id":316,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",6]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"但我们没有亲口听到她这么告诉我们。","id":317,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",6]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"她必须亲口告诉我们，她的想法。","id":318,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",6]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"只有这样，当我们努力的最后结果依然是她要离开，那时，我才能心甘情愿地和她告别呀。","id":319,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",6]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"我努力过了，我不后悔的。","id":320,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":321},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"......啊，大概还是会后悔吧，但不会那么后悔。","id":322,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":323},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝纳尔多","text":"你很有智慧，空小姐。","id":324,"figure":["avg_npc_685_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":325},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"我只是给自己的逞强找点借口而已啦。","id":326,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",8]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"不过，和您这么说了一通之后，我也感觉好多了。","id":327,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",8]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"确实，现在即使我真的能见她，恐怕什么也帮不了她。","id":328,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":329},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝纳尔多","text":"实际上，我都已经准备同意你的要求了。","id":330,"figure":["avg_npc_685_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝纳尔多","text":"在审判之后，你会见到她的，我保证。","id":331,"figure":["avg_npc_685_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":332},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"真的吗！","id":333,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":334},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝纳尔多","text":"不过现在，可能还要再等等。","id":335,"figure":["avg_npc_685_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":336},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"谢谢您，在那之前，我会好好准备的。","id":337,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":338},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝纳尔多","text":"呵呵。","id":339,"figure":["avg_npc_685_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝纳尔多","text":"真遗憾，我不能亲眼看到你的首秀了。","id":340,"figure":["avg_npc_685_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":341},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"欸？您不看吗？","id":342,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":343},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝纳尔多","text":"是啊，那天，我恐怕会有一些重要的事情要处理。","id":344,"figure":["avg_npc_685_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝纳尔多","text":"但是，你可以放心，我已经为你准备好了最好的舞台。","id":345,"figure":["avg_npc_685_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":346},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"谢谢！","id":347,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",8]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"那我就先回去了。","id":348,"figure":["avg_npc_684_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_684_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":349},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝纳尔多","text":"去吧。","id":350,"figure":["avg_npc_685_1",7]},{"type":"dialog","id":351},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.7","id":352},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#8$1","name2":"char_empty","fadetime":"1","id":353},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":354},{"type":"playsound","key":"$doorclosequite","id":355},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":356},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#6$1","name2":"char_empty","fadetime":"1","id":357},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝纳尔多","text":"......","id":358,"figure":["avg_npc_685_1",5]},{"type":"character","id":359},{"type":"text","text":"贝纳尔多走到书架边，从书架上抽出一本书。","id":360},{"type":"text","text":"那是一本环绕着荆棘的法典。","id":361},{"type":"text","text":"他沉默良久，最后，拨通一个电话。","id":362},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_telephone","id":363},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":364},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_685_1#2$1","id":365},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝纳尔多","text":"......德米特，告诉她，就说，我答应了。","id":366,"figure":["avg_npc_685_1",1]},{"type":"character","id":367},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_thunders_amb","volume":"0.5","id":368},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_thunders_amb","volume":"0.3","Delay":"0.7","channel":"a","id":369},{"type":"text","text":"“轰”的一声，窗外，雷声翻涌。","id":370},{"type":"text","text":"像是在预告着，大雨将至。","id":371},{"type":"dialog","id":372},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":373},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":374},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":375},{"type":"character","id":376},{"type":"image","id":377}],"characters":[